metadata.name: Demonic History Chapter 1
metadata.description: Back in ancient times, there was a demon. Beautiful young girl with small horns. She lived in a beautiful forest thinking about her future and where she came from. And lived in that forest and a dragon who knew about everything in the world. Demon decided to make friends with the dragon that he could tell her the stories of the night. They were friends for a short time until people invaded their territory and began to threaten to kill them. People were not afraid of the dragon, but they was afraid demon very much, they were afraid so much that they decided to threaten the dragon that they would kill him if he did not catch and seal it. That's what the dragon did. But the demon knew how to get out of the flask.
